    "message": "Invalid value at 'trigger.repository_event_config.repository_type' (type.googleapis.com/google.devtools.cloudbuild.v1.RepositoryEventConfig.RepositoryType), \"GITLAB\"\nInvalid JSON payload received. Unknown name \"repositoryType\" at 'trigger.source_to_build': Cannot find field.\nInvalid JSON payload received. Unknown name \"repositoryType\" at 'trigger.git_file_source': Cannot find field.",
    "status": "INVALID_ARGUMENT",
    "details": [
